      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Atos 首席执行官因战略纠纷在任三个月后辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/atos-ceo-quits-over-strategy-dispute-amid-refinancing-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Atos SE 任命 Paul Saleh 接替 Yves Bernaert 担任首席执行官，此前董事会与即将卸任的领导人在这家陷入困境的科技公司的扭亏为盈战略上存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/atos-ceo-quits-over-strategy-dispute-amid-refinancing-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 08:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车为电动汽车提供 7,500 美元现金奖励，以匹配美国税收抵免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/hyundai-offers-7-500-cash-bonus-for-evs-to-match-us-tax-credits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车公司将为美国电动汽车购买者提供高达 7,500 美元的现金奖励，以保持其汽车与根据乔·拜登总统的通货膨胀削减法案有资格获得税收抵免的汽车制造商的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/hyundai-offers-7-500-cash-bonus-for-evs-to-match-us-tax-credits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:46:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SoftwareOne 拒绝 35 亿美元的收购要约后股价下跌 13%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/softwareone-rebuffs-bain-s-bid-will-remain-standalone-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SoftwareOne Holding AG 股价创下近两年来最大跌幅，此前这家瑞士 IT 公司拒绝了贝恩资本对其估值为 29.8 亿瑞士法郎（35 亿美元）的收购要约，结束了数月的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/softwareone-rebuffs-bain-s-bid-will-remain-standalone-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国拟斥资 4700 亿美元建设芯片制造中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/south-korea-lays-out-470-billion-plan-to-build-chipmaking-hub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国公布了三星电子和 SK 海力士等领先企业计划斥资超过 4700 亿美元建立全球最大芯片制造集群的计划，加入保障国内供应的全球竞赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/south-korea-lays-out-470-billion-plan-to-build-chipmaking-hub</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度科技巨头市值在短短两天内增加了 220 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/wipro-jumps-10-after-3q-earnings-signal-recovery-in-tech-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度软件巨头的股价在新的一年伊始就开始飙升，上季度高于预期的销售额让投资者感到惊讶，并帮助提振了该行业的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/wipro-jumps-10-after-3q-earnings-signal-recovery-in-tech-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管百度否认与解放军人工智能有联系，但其跌幅为 2022 年以来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/baidu-dives-most-since-2022-after-report-links-ai-to-china-s-pla</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告将百度的 Ernie AI 平台与关键军事研究联系起来，引发了人们对华盛顿报复的担忧，导致百度股价跌至一年多以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/baidu-dives-most-since-2022-after-report-links-ai-to-china-s-pla</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 02:11:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
